  "description": "\u00c2\u00a9 Copyright 2018 Blue Cross and Blue Shield of Kansas City\n\nCalled by:\n                    \n\nPROCESSING : Reads data from the SavRx Claim file and creats a common output\n\nModifications:                        \n Developer                           Date              Project/Altiris #    Change Description                                       Development Project    Code Reviewer         Date Reviewed\n---------------------------------------     -------------------   ------------------------    -------------------------------------------------------------------   ----------------------------------   -----------------------------    -------------------------   \nKaushik Kapoor                   2018-03-30    5828                    Initial Programming                                         EnterpriseDev2            Kalyan Neelam          2018-04-20\nKaushik Kapoor                   2018-09-10    5828                    Changed the calculation column to PD_DT   EnterpriseDev2            Hugh Sisson             2018-09-19\n\nAnnotations:\nThis job extracts data from LDI claims file and load file date and other required details in to a common layout for further use."
